<title>COME, HOLY SPIRIT, COME</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hungin, Thagau Thiengtho,
 Na vak hawih hung vak hen;
 Ka lunggil thimnau nawhmang in,
 Ka mituh hihvak in.

[V2]
 2. Ka ginnau hihat in,
 Ginlah, lauh lamang in;
 Lungsietna thi thei ngeilo chuh,
 Lunggil ah hih kuongin.

[V3]
 3. Gitloh ei hetsak in,
 Thisan ah ei puiin;
 Pathien hehpih ka lung u ah,
 Chien takin latsak in.

[V4]
 4. Lunggil suk thiengthona,
 Thagau suk thienthona;
 Hinna thak piek haw Nang maia,
 Na siemthak vek thei hi.

[V5]
 5. Ka lungu ah chengin,
 Lung gikpuok lamang in;
 Hun he'n, hun lungsiet hun pak kau,
 Pa, Chapa leh Nangmah.</lyrics>
</song>